A) Has a negative impact on NPV because we anticipate the depreciation expense, which has a negative impact on EBIT;
B) Has a positive impact on NPV because we anticipate the depreciation tax shield, which has a positive impact on the present value of free cash flows;
C) Has no impact on NPV, because depreciation is a non-cash expense;
D) None of the above.
